Author: roseology
Text: I totally feel the same way when I do that :/ just did tonight, actually. It helps me to tell myself the extra calories go to nourishing my body and hopefully repairing the damage I have caused it. Then, my ED brain comforts itself by telling me that everything I eat requires energy expenditure to burn and therefore being over slightly won’t matter because I technically ate less calories than I recorded lol.  Just know your body needs the calories and going over a little won’t hurt it in the long run!!
